data.description: Enchanting Country get-away on just over 3 acres with 2 homes and an in-ground pool!! This beautiful home offers a refuge from the hustle and bustle from it's spacious 4 Bed/3.5 Bath primary home, large in-ground swimming pool, garage/workshop, storage shed, second 3/2 MH behind the main home and 3.39 acres of unrestricted land! This home is set to charm with it's two living/entertaining spaces, one featuring a w/b stove, split-floor plan, comfy kitchen with natural lighting and 3.5 baths for no early morning traffic jams between kiddos. This lovely home also offers a 2 car detached garage/workshop with a storage/carport overhang and an entire extra home at the rear of the property! The double wide mobile home features 3 bed/2 baths and offers the potential for additional family members or even rental property to be closely overseen. Relax in the completely fenced in-ground pool ready for the hot Texas summer just around the corner! Call for more info!
